sequenceDiagram
    participant Patient
    participant ReportsPage as Reports Page
    participant OCR as OCR Service
    participant Parser
    participant DB as Database

    Patient->>ReportsPage: Upload File
    ReportsPage->>OCR: Extract Text
    OCR-->>ReportsPage: Extracted Text
    ReportsPage->>Parser: Parse Lab Values
    Parser-->>ReportsPage: Structured Data

    alt Extract Success
        ReportsPage->>DB: Save Report + Values
        DB-->>ReportsPage: Success
        ReportsPage->>Patient: Show "Report Added"

    else Extraction Failed
        ReportsPage->>Patient: Show Manual Entry Form
    end
